quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  33,63,"Abandu bakhurebanga okhulondokhana nende indukho, boola mbu: “Obumanyi bwayo buli khu Nyasaye butswa, ne nishina shitsa okhukhumanyisia mbu khawundi indukho ili ahambi?”"
  33,64,"Toto Nyasaye yara eshilamo khubakhayi, ne yabarecheshela omulilo kusambanga muno."
  33,65,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, ne shibalinyoola omuhelwa nohomba omukhonyi tawe."
  33,66,"Inyanga yobweni bwabu bulikalukhanibwa mumulilo, baliboola mbu: “Abaane, khumanyangakhwo khwawulila Nyasaye, mana khwawulila Omurumwa.”"
  33,67,"Ne baliboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, toto efwe khwaulila Abaami befu nende Abakhongo befu, mana nibakhukosia Injila."
  33,68,"Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, bahelesie eshinyasio eshikhabili, ne obaheresye eshilamo eshikhongo.”"
  33,69,"Enywe Abasuubila, mulaba shinga balia abasinyisia Musa, mana Nyasaye namutswenula ehale nende kababoola, naye yali weshiribwa imbeli wa Nyasaye."
  33,70,"Enywe balia basuubila, rie Nyasaye, ne boole amakhuwa katoto."
  33,71,"Alabakasilia ebikhole bienyu ne alabaleshela ebionoono bienyu. Ne ulia uwulila Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, toto alaba naburire okhubura okhukhongo."
  33,72,"Toto efwe khwalolesia amalako kefu khu likulu nende eshialo nende efikulu, mana nibikhaya okhukachinga mana nibikaria, mana Omundu nakachinga. Toto ye ni omwonooni omukhongo, omusilu muno."
  33,73,"Kho Nyasaye anyoole okhuhelesia eshinyasio abeshikhabili Abasatsa nende abeshikhabili Abakhasi, nende abatsokaasi beshisatsa nende abatsokaasi beshikhasi, ne aleshele abasubili abasatsa nende abasubili abakhasi. Ne toto Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi po."